{"id":"0fb47f3e81880cb7c6791ee4f88ba0b1d0dca012","url":"https://openaim.pramit.gg/","title":"OpenAim","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"Hacker News (黑客新闻)","byline":null,"excerpt":"Arena moodEarned backdrop palettes — free play only. Locked ones show what unlocks them.","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div>\n          <section id=\"sec-appearance\" data-sec=\"Appearance\">\n            <P><h3>Appearance</h3></P>\n            <label>\n              <span>Theme</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Target color<small>Presets are colorblind-friendly against every theme.</small></span>\n              <span>\n                \n                \n              </span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Target style</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Playfield background</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <div>\n              <p><span>Arena mood<small>Earned backdrop palettes — free play only. Locked ones show what unlocks them.</small></span></p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <p><span>Target finish<small>Earned target skins — free play only. Rated drills always use the standard target.</small></span></p>\n            </div>\n            <label>\n              <span>Living scene<small>Backdrop shifts between drills &amp; drifts slowly to fight visual fatigue. Never touches targets or contrast.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Reduced eye strain<small>Dims &amp; warms the scene and UI for long sessions — lowers luminance load. Targets keep full contrast.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Motion<small>Reduce disables UI transitions; Auto follows your OS.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-crosshair\" data-sec=\"Crosshair\">\n            <P><h3>Crosshair</h3></P>\n            <label>\n              <span>Style</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Size</span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-xh-size\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Thickness</span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-xh-thick\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Gap</span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-xh-gap\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Color</span>\n              <span>\n                <label> <span>theme</span></label>\n                \n              </span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Outline<small>Keeps the crosshair visible over targets.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>On-target reaction<small>Off by default for clean telemetry.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-feedback\" data-sec=\"Feedback\">\n            <P><h3>Feedback</h3></P>\n            <label>\n              <span>Hit marker</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Hit sound</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Volume</span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-volume\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Miss flash<small>Red flick at the crosshair on a missed shot.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Shot feedback sounds<small>Missed shots and magazine reloads.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Blocked-shot cue<small>Multi-tap drills cap the fire rate. Marks pulls that came too early to fire, so they read as your timing, not lag.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Tracking tone<small>Sustained lock tone that climbs while your crosshair holds a target.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Off-screen spawn cue<small>Panned alert pointing to targets that spawn out of view.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Off-screen spawn marker<small>A brief edge chevron toward a target that spawns out of view — the visual twin of the spawn cue.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Pace metronome<small>Coached drills: one beat per pace budget.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Reward moments<small>Confetti + a flourish when you set a record, rank up, or hit a streak.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Eye-rest reminders<small>A gentle 20-20-20 nudge between drills on long sessions.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>HUD elements</span>\n              <span>\n                <label> <span>timer</span></label>\n                <label> <span>score</span></label>\n                <label> <span>acc</span></label>\n                <label> <span>fps</span></label>\n              </span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Zen mode<small>Hide the whole HUD during runs; results still show everything.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-input\" data-sec=\"Input\">\n            <P><h3>Input &amp; camera</h3></P>\n            <label>\n              <span>Sensitivity<small>° per mouse count.</small></span>\n              <span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Mouse DPI<small>Optional. Enables cm/360 and hand-travel modeling.</small></span>\n              <span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Import sens<small>Converts your in-game sensitivity.</small></span>\n              <span>\n                <!-- options are filled from GAME_YAW at wire-up (settings-panel.ts) -->\n                \n                <!-- shown only for multiplier games (R6); wired in settings-panel.ts -->\n                \n                \n                \n              </span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Field of view<small>Horizontal; stamped into every replay.</small></span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-fov\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Invert Y</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <p><span>Raw input<small>Whether the browser delivers unaccelerated mouse motion. OpenAim never accelerates; this is the browser/OS layer.</small></span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-rawinput\"></span></span>\n            </p>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-coach\" data-sec=\"Coach\">\n            <P><h3>Coach</h3></P>\n            <label>\n              <span>Challenge point<small>Target success rate drills are solved to.</small></span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-challenge\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            \n            <label>\n              <span>Explanations<small>Full detail always stays behind the ? chip.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Session length<small>Drills per coached session.</small></span>\n              <span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Focus<small>Let the coach choose, or lock the session to one axis.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>AutoGain<small>Sens auto-tuning from measured under/overshoot.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-data\" data-sec=\"Data\">\n            <P><h3>Data</h3></P>\n            <label>\n              <span>Capture level<small>Summary skips raw mouse/camera streams; deep analysis needs Full.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Auto-download replay<small>Save the .oar after every completed run.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <p><span>Your data</span>\n              <span>\n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n              </span>\n            </p>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-commons\" data-sec=\"Commons\">\n            <P><h3>Aim Commons</h3></P>\n            <p id=\"commons-note\">\n              Anonymous drill summaries are contributed by default to train the shared,\n              science-based player model everyone starts from and that renormalizes your ratings\n              to real peers. No raw mouse traces, no identity, no device info — and you can opt out\n              or revoke below anytime. Raw replays and the public leaderboard stay off unless you\n              turn them on.\n            </p>\n            <label>\n              <span>Contribute runs<small>Sends drill summaries + capability features (no raw mouse, no device info) to sharpen the population model everyone starts from.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Leaderboard<small>Rank on the task-Elo boards under a public handle.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Handle<small>Your public leaderboard name.</small></span>\n              <span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Share replays<small>Advanced: uploads raw mouse-movement traces (mildly biometric) for deeper analysis and spectating. Requires the two above.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <p><span>Status<small id=\"commons-status\">local only</small></span>\n              <span>\n                \n              </span>\n            </p>\n          </section>\n          <p>\n            Settings that change the meaning of telemetry (FOV, sens, target style, crosshair, invert, capture level)\n            are recorded in each replay's .oar header, so analysis reflects the settings the run used.\n          </p>\n          </div></DIV>","content_text":"Appearance Theme Target colorPresets are colorblind-friendly against every theme. Target style Playfield background Arena moodEarned backdrop palettes — free play only. Locked ones show what unlocks them. Target finishEarned target skins — free play only. Rated drills always use the standard target. Living sceneBackdrop shifts between drills & drifts slowly to fight visual fatigue. Never touches targets or contrast. Reduced eye strainDims & warms the scene and UI for long sessions — lowers luminance load. Targets keep full contrast. MotionReduce disables UI transitions; Auto follows your OS. Crosshair Style Size Thickness Gap Color theme OutlineKeeps the crosshair visible over targets. On-target reactionOff by default for clean telemetry. Feedback Hit marker Hit sound Volume Miss flashRed flick at the crosshair on a missed shot. Shot feedback soundsMissed shots and magazine reloads. Blocked-shot cueMulti-tap drills cap the fire rate. Marks pulls that came too early to fire, so they read as your timing, not lag. Tracking toneSustained lock tone that climbs while your crosshair holds a target. Off-screen spawn cuePanned alert pointing to targets that spawn out of view. Off-screen spawn markerA brief edge chevron toward a target that spawns out of view — the visual twin of the spawn cue. Pace metronomeCoached drills: one beat per pace budget. Reward momentsConfetti + a flourish when you set a record, rank up, or hit a streak. Eye-rest remindersA gentle 20-20-20 nudge between drills on long sessions. HUD elements timer score acc fps Zen modeHide the whole HUD during runs; results still show everything. Input & camera Sensitivity° per mouse count. Mouse DPIOptional. Enables cm/360 and hand-travel modeling. Import sensConverts your in-game sensitivity. Field of viewHorizontal; stamped into every replay. Invert Y Raw inputWhether the browser delivers unaccelerated mouse motion. OpenAim never accelerates; this is the browser/OS layer. Coach Challenge pointTarget success rate drills are solved to. ExplanationsFull detail always stays behind the ? chip. Session lengthDrills per coached session. FocusLet the coach choose, or lock the session to one axis. AutoGainSens auto-tuning from measured under/overshoot. Data Capture levelSummary skips raw mouse/camera streams; deep analysis needs Full. Auto-download replaySave the .oar after every completed run. Your data Aim Commons Anonymous drill summaries are contributed by default to train the shared, science-based player model everyone starts from and that renormalizes your ratings to real peers. No raw mouse traces, no identity, no device info — and you can opt out or revoke below anytime. Raw replays and the public leaderboard stay off unless you turn them on. Contribute runsSends drill summaries + capability features (no raw mouse, no device info) to sharpen the population model everyone starts from. LeaderboardRank on the task-Elo boards under a public handle. HandleYour public leaderboard name. Share replaysAdvanced: uploads raw mouse-movement traces (mildly biometric) for deeper analysis and spectating. Requires the two above. Statuslocal only Settings that change the meaning of telemetry (FOV, sens, target style, crosshair, invert, capture level) are recorded in each replay's .oar header, so analysis reflects the settings the run used.","fetched_at":"2026-07-22T06:58:47.812Z","ok":true,"blocks":[{"html_en":"<h3>Appearance</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Appearance","zh":"外貌"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Arena mood<small>Earned backdrop palettes — free play only. Locked ones show what unlocks them.</small></span></p>","sentences":[{"en":"Arena moodEarned backdrop palettes — free play only.","zh":"竞技场心情赢得的背景调色板 - 仅限免费游戏。"},{"en":"Locked ones show what unlocks them.","zh":"锁定的会显示什么可以解锁它们。"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Target finish<small>Earned target skins — free play only. Rated drills always use the standard target.</small></span></p>","sentences":[{"en":"Target finishEarned target skins — free play only.","zh":"目标完成获得的目标皮肤——仅限免费游戏。"},{"en":"Rated drills always use the standard target.","zh":"额定钻头始终使用标准目标。"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Crosshair</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Crosshair","zh":"十字线"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Feedback</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Feedback","zh":"反馈"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Input &amp; camera</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Input & camera","zh":"输入和摄像头"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Raw input<small>Whether the browser delivers unaccelerated mouse motion. OpenAim never accelerates; this is the browser/OS layer.</small></span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-rawinput\"></span></span>\n            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Raw inputWhether the browser delivers unaccelerated mouse motion.","zh":"原始输入浏览器是否提供不加速的鼠标运动。"},{"en":"OpenAim never accelerates; this is the browser/OS layer.","zh":"OpenAim 永远不会加速；这是浏览器/操作系统层。"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Coach</h3>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<h3>Data</h3>","sentences":[]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Your data</span>\n              <span>\n                \n                \n                \n                \n                \n              </span>\n            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Your data","zh":"您的数据"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Aim Commons</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Aim Commons","zh":"目标共享"}]},{"html_en":"<p id=\"commons-note\">\n              Anonymous drill summaries are contributed by default to train the shared,\n              science-based player model everyone starts from and that renormalizes your ratings\n              to real peers. No raw mouse traces, no identity, no device info — and you can opt out\n              or revoke below anytime. Raw replays and the public leaderboard stay off unless you\n              turn them on.\n            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Anonymous drill summaries are contributed by default to train the shared, science-based player model everyone starts from and that renormalizes your ratings to real peers.","zh":"默认情况下，会提供匿名训练摘要，以训练每个人都开始的共享的、基于科学的玩家模型，并将您的评分重新规范为真实的同行。"},{"en":"No raw mouse traces, no identity, no device info — and you can opt out or revoke below anytime.","zh":"没有原始鼠标痕迹，没有身份，没有设备信息 - 您可以随时选择退出或撤销。"},{"en":"Raw replays and the public leaderboard stay off unless you turn them on.","zh":"除非您将其打开，否则原始重播和公共排行榜将保持关闭状态。"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>Status<small id=\"commons-status\">local only</small></span>\n              <span>\n                \n              </span>\n            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Statuslocal only","zh":"仅限本地状态"}]},{"html_en":"<p>\n            Settings that change the meaning of telemetry (FOV, sens, target style, crosshair, invert, capture level)\n            are recorded in each replay's .oar header, so analysis reflects the settings the run used.\n          </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Settings that change the meaning of telemetry (FOV, sens, target style, crosshair, invert, capture level) are recorded in each replay's .oar header, so analysis reflects the settings the run used.","zh":"更改遥测含义的设置（FOV、Sens、目标样式、十字准线、反转、捕获级别）记录在每个回放的 .oar 标头中，因此分析反映了运行所使用的设置。"}]}],"translated":true,"content_html_zh":"<div class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div>\n          <section id=\"sec-appearance\" data-sec=\"Appearance\">\n            <p></p><h3>外貌</h3><p></p>\n            <label>\n              <span>Theme</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Target color<small>Presets are colorblind-friendly against every theme.</small></span>\n              <span>\n                \n                \n              </span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Target style</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Playfield background</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <div>\n              <p>竞技场心情赢得的背景调色板 - 仅限免费游戏。 锁定的会显示什么可以解锁它们。</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <p>目标完成获得的目标皮肤——仅限免费游戏。 额定钻头始终使用标准目标。</p>\n            </div>\n            <label>\n              <span>Living scene<small>Backdrop shifts between drills &amp; drifts slowly to fight visual fatigue. Never touches targets or contrast.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Reduced eye strain<small>Dims &amp; warms the scene and UI for long sessions — lowers luminance load. Targets keep full contrast.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Motion<small>Reduce disables UI transitions; Auto follows your OS.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-crosshair\" data-sec=\"Crosshair\">\n            <p></p><h3>十字线</h3><p></p>\n            <label>\n              <span>Style</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Size</span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-xh-size\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Thickness</span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-xh-thick\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Gap</span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-xh-gap\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Color</span>\n              <span>\n                <label> <span>theme</span></label>\n                \n              </span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Outline<small>Keeps the crosshair visible over targets.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>On-target reaction<small>Off by default for clean telemetry.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-feedback\" data-sec=\"Feedback\">\n            <p></p><h3>反馈</h3><p></p>\n            <label>\n              <span>Hit marker</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Hit sound</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Volume</span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-volume\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Miss flash<small>Red flick at the crosshair on a missed shot.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Shot feedback sounds<small>Missed shots and magazine reloads.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Blocked-shot cue<small>Multi-tap drills cap the fire rate. Marks pulls that came too early to fire, so they read as your timing, not lag.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Tracking tone<small>Sustained lock tone that climbs while your crosshair holds a target.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Off-screen spawn cue<small>Panned alert pointing to targets that spawn out of view.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Off-screen spawn marker<small>A brief edge chevron toward a target that spawns out of view — the visual twin of the spawn cue.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Pace metronome<small>Coached drills: one beat per pace budget.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Reward moments<small>Confetti + a flourish when you set a record, rank up, or hit a streak.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Eye-rest reminders<small>A gentle 20-20-20 nudge between drills on long sessions.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>HUD elements</span>\n              <span>\n                <label> <span>timer</span></label>\n                <label> <span>score</span></label>\n                <label> <span>acc</span></label>\n                <label> <span>fps</span></label>\n              </span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Zen mode<small>Hide the whole HUD during runs; results still show everything.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-input\" data-sec=\"Input\">\n            <p></p><h3>输入和摄像头</h3><p></p>\n            <label>\n              <span>Sensitivity<small>° per mouse count.</small></span>\n              <span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Mouse DPI<small>Optional. Enables cm/360 and hand-travel modeling.</small></span>\n              <span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Import sens<small>Converts your in-game sensitivity.</small></span>\n              <span>\n                <!-- options are filled from GAME_YAW at wire-up (settings-panel.ts) -->\n                \n                <!-- shown only for multiplier games (R6); wired in settings-panel.ts -->\n                \n                \n                \n              </span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Field of view<small>Horizontal; stamped into every replay.</small></span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-fov\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Invert Y</span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <p>原始输入浏览器是否提供不加速的鼠标运动。 OpenAim 永远不会加速；这是浏览器/操作系统层。</p>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-coach\" data-sec=\"Coach\">\n            <p></p><h3>Coach</h3><p></p>\n            <label>\n              <span>Challenge point<small>Target success rate drills are solved to.</small></span>\n              <span><span id=\"val-challenge\"></span></span>\n            </label>\n            \n            <label>\n              <span>Explanations<small>Full detail always stays behind the ? chip.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Session length<small>Drills per coached session.</small></span>\n              <span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Focus<small>Let the coach choose, or lock the session to one axis.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>AutoGain<small>Sens auto-tuning from measured under/overshoot.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-data\" data-sec=\"Data\">\n            <p></p><h3>Data</h3><p></p>\n            <label>\n              <span>Capture level<small>Summary skips raw mouse/camera streams; deep analysis needs Full.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Auto-download replay<small>Save the .oar after every completed run.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <p>您的数据</p>\n          </section>\n\n          <section id=\"sec-commons\" data-sec=\"Commons\">\n            <p></p><h3>目标共享</h3><p></p>\n            <p id=\"commons-note\">默认情况下，会提供匿名训练摘要，以训练每个人都开始的共享的、基于科学的玩家模型，并将您的评分重新规范为真实的同行。 没有原始鼠标痕迹，没有身份，没有设备信息 - 您可以随时选择退出或撤销。 除非您将其打开，否则原始重播和公共排行榜将保持关闭状态。</p>\n            <label>\n              <span>Contribute runs<small>Sends drill summaries + capability features (no raw mouse, no device info) to sharpen the population model everyone starts from.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Leaderboard<small>Rank on the task-Elo boards under a public handle.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Handle<small>Your public leaderboard name.</small></span>\n              <span></span>\n            </label>\n            <label>\n              <span>Share replays<small>Advanced: uploads raw mouse-movement traces (mildly biometric) for deeper analysis and spectating. Requires the two above.</small></span>\n              \n            </label>\n            <p>仅限本地状态</p>\n          </section>\n          <p>更改遥测含义的设置（FOV、Sens、目标样式、十字准线、反转、捕获级别）记录在每个回放的 .oar 标头中，因此分析反映了运行所使用的设置。</p>\n          </div></div>"}